#31687
the Norstar Beacon's Lamplighter Quarters~
   A very conservative living quarters is before you.  The room is extremely
well organized and is very clean, dust free and polished.  A plethora of
replacement parts for the beacon are organized on a well-crafted shelving
system to the north.  To the east you find a bed, nightstand and a reading
chair.  The southern wall is a workstation, there are hundreds of tools on the
wall behind a pristine workbench.  A small wood-burning stove burns dimly in
the southeastern corner.  
~
