#31694
Norstar Beacon Lantern Room~
   This room is positioned at the top of the Norstar Beacon.  From here you
can see very far into the distance on a clear day.  There is a large lamp
suspended in front of a few directional mirrors.  They seem very well
maintained, polished, and streakless.  This lamp is pointing northward and
serves as a way for those who find themselves lost in the tundra to navigate
back towards the warmth of the south.  A small stove sits in the southern part
of the room burning dimly compared to the lamp.  
~
